  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      A patient referred to have a lesion in the stomach removed. The aims of this study are to
      collect information on the technique of endoscopic removal of such lesions. By collecting
      information on a large number of patients undergoing this procedure the investigators can
      determine the best ways of diagnosing and removing these lesions safely and effectively.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
